title: HPE 3PAR: Ports
agents: 3par
catalog: hw/storagehw/hpe
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check displays the state of a connection, the associated
 WWN and the mode. If there is information about it, it will
 display also the failover state and the label of this port.

 The service state depends on the link and failover state.
 You can define the service state for each possible value a port can
 have.

inventory:
 One service is created for each port connection.
